Interface DataStream

  • All Superinterfaces:
    OnComplete, net.named_data.jndn.OnData, OnException, net.named_data.jndn.OnTimeout
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SegmentedDataStream

    public interface DataStream
extends net.named_data.jndn.OnData, net.named_data.jndn.OnTimeout, OnComplete, OnException
    Define a stream of Data packets as they are retrieved from the network and provide methods for observing stream events
